title: Madsen - Full Discography 2011
description:
Madsen is a rock band from Priesseck, a district of Clenze (Wendland), Germany. Three of them are brothers, so the band name is the same as the family name: Madsen. Their music contains elements of rock, punk, and pop, with german lyrics.
